          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">4.1 Facebook Login and Authentication</h3>
          <p>When you choose to access our services using Facebook Login, we integrate with Meta's authentication system to provide you with a seamless experience. This integration:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>Allows you to log in using your existing Facebook credentials</li>
            <li>Eliminates the need to create and remember separate login credentials</li>
            <li>Enables us to verify your identity through Meta's secure authentication system</li>
            <li>Provides access to basic profile information that you have made available</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">4.2 Data Minimization and Purpose Limitation</h3>
          <p>We adhere to strict data minimization principles for Meta platform integrations:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Minimal Data Collection:</strong> We only request access to information that is essential for our service functionality</li>
            <li><strong>Purpose-Specific Use:</strong> Data obtained from Meta platforms is used solely for the purposes disclosed at the time of collection</li>
            <li><strong>No Excessive Permissions:</strong> We do not request broad permissions that exceed our legitimate business needs</li>
            <li><strong>Regular Review:</strong> We periodically review and minimize the data we collect and retain</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">4.3 Meta App Permissions and Controls</h3>
          <p>You maintain control over your data and our app's access to your Meta account:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li><strong>Permission Management:</strong> You can review and modify app permissions at any time through your Facebook App Settings</li>
            <li><strong>Data Access Control:</strong> You can limit what information our app can access from your profile</li>
            <li><strong>Revocation Rights:</strong> You can revoke our app's access to your account at any time</li>
            <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We clearly explain what data we access and why during the authorization process</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">4.4 Compliance with Meta Policies</h3>
          <p>Our Meta platform integrations comply with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>Meta's Platform Policy and Terms of Service</li>
            <li>Facebook's Data Policy and Privacy Standards</li>
            <li>App Store and platform-specific guidelines</li>
            <li>Applicable privacy laws and regulations (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-6 mb-3">4.5 Data Deletion for Meta Connected Apps and WhatsApp</h3>
          <p>If you wish to delete data associated with our Meta-connected applications or WhatsApp interactions:</p>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mt-4 mb-2">Facebook/Meta Apps:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>You can disconnect our app from your Facebook account through Facebook's App Settings</li>
            <li>Upon disconnection, we will delete your associated data within 30 days</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mt-4 mb-2">WhatsApp Data:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>Block our WhatsApp Business number to stop receiving messages</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your conversation history by sending "DELETE MY DATA" to our WhatsApp Business account</li>
            <li>We will delete your WhatsApp conversation data, including messages, media, and phone number, within 30 days</li>
            <li>Note: Some message metadata may be retained for legal compliance or fraud prevention (anonymized)</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-medium mt-4 mb-2">General Data Deletion:</h4>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>You can also request direct data deletion by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@neudayai.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">privacy@neudayai.com</a></li>
            <li>For detailed instructions, please refer to our <a href="/data-deletion" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 underline">Data Deletion Instructions</a></li>
          </ul>
          
